## How to set up apache virtual site

1. Edit "vineyard.site" file and enter correct root path in DocumentRoot and <Directory> entries

2. Copy "vineyard.site" in /etc/apache2/sites-available

3. Add "vineyard.dev" as alias of localhost (127.0.0.1) in /etc/hosts

4. Enable Apache site: sudo a2ensite vineyard.site

5. Visit http://vineyard.dev/

6. Enjoy!
